kai-assistant (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Major release: Production-ready voice assistant
  * Voice-optimized LLM responses (no markdown in speech)
  * Conversation mode (stay awake for follow-up questions)
  * Keyboard interrupt support (press SPACE to stop)
  * Volume control and audio device selection
  * Complete Debian packaging with isolated dependencies
  * Improved TTS streaming with proper interrupt handling
  * Better error handling and debug output

 -- Kai Contributors <kai@example.com>  Mon, 01 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000

kai-assistant (0.9.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Voice interaction with wake word detection
  * Local LLM integration via Ollama
  * Plugin system for extensibility
  * GUI settings interface

 -- Kai Contributors <kai@example.com>  Mon, 01 Dec 2025 00:00:00 +0000
